spokane wash he and his wife jean are running a tshirt stand 
for spokanes latus motors harleydavidson for the fourth year 
everyone we talked to said oh my buddy didnt show up 
because hes waiting for next year paull said 
during the rally main street and two other thoroughfares are 
taken over by vendors like the paulls selling every kind of biker 
