army in a telephone call with parents larry and lynne swanson he 
said he became fed up with guerrillas rebel yells and communist 
indoctrination 
he was questioned rather heavily at first and then later i 
think they tried to influence him a bit his mother said he 
said he got so sick of revolutionary music and stories of ambush he 
started to complain so they stopped 
