this northern suburb of boston 
aardu bounded out of his cage july 23 and headed for the 
middlesex fells a 3000acre wooded preserve nearby zoo officials 
said the 18monthold aardu a hardy vegetarian could have 
survived for months in the woods if necessary 
whether he will survive state budget cuts is another matter the 
zoo is due to close in april 1991 ilyas bhatti commissioner of 
