repercussions in the region but did not elaborate 
another group of arab nations that includes saudi arabia later 
issued a similar condemnation the group the gulf cooperation 
council also includes qatar oman bahrain the united arab 
emirates and kuwait 
we strongly condemn and are very sorry for this attack that 
one arab state took against another arab state the groups 
statement said after its representatives met in cairo 
