at the start of wynkoops senior year he was forced to leave 
the school because he had gotten married over the summer the 
summer of 1925 
he could have returned the next year as a married student but 
ended up waiting more than 60 years to complete the seven credits 
he needed for a yale degree 
i finally had the time and the money i asked my brother a 
1928 yale graduate what i ought to do with it and he said why 
