allegheny international reported a loss of 351 per share 
compared with a net loss of 153 million or 210 a share in the 
yearago period 
sales increased 1 percent to 2373 million from 2349 million 
for the fiscal 1990 ninemonth period the company reported a 
net loss of 426 million or 589 a share compared with a loss 
of 182 million or 375 a share in the yearago period 
sales in the ninemonth period fell 3 percent to 7048 million 
from 7302 million 
